snippet.title: Burst Fighter- 2nd Trailer  -Magesoft
snippet.description:
Burst Fighter is a fast paced Shmups game with customizable unit parts.
Your main purpose is to survive from all the enemy hordes & reclaim your homeland.

Checkout our demo at magesoft.itch.io
